      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, ideally for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts. It has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that requires immediate attention. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust and dents, while the interior has substantial tearing and staining. It will require a trailer for transport as it is not currently roadworthy.",
