      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive excellence, maintained to a rigorous standard of mechanical and aesthetic quality. This vehicle offers a refined driving experience, characterized by its consistent performance and a well-preserved interior that reflects diligent ownership. We invite you to acquire a machine that expertly balances sophisticated engineering with enduring value, ensuring a premier standard of transport for its next proprietor.",
      "price": 29500.0,
